## MDX conventions

Use Starlight components where appropriate:

```mdx
import { Card, CardGrid } from '@astrojs/starlight/components';

:::note[Label]
Content
:::

:::caution[Label]
Content
:::
```

Use tables for reference material. Use `:::caution` for the GBI score direction warning wherever GBI is introduced for the first time on a page.

## Content rules

- If unsure about a framework definition, ask before writing — ARAF terms have specific meanings
- Never add certification tiers, dimension names, or GBI thresholds that differ from the definitions above
- The site should be citable in regulatory submissions and policy papers — accuracy matters
- Version references in content should say "ARAF v2.1" — version is not part of the logo lockup
- Standard governance does not constitute assessor accreditation, certification 